R.VALUE
=======
* Version used for launching the validation published in the VALUE Portal
* Redefined index and measure calculation routines to be applied on vectors
* Created a wrapper function to launch the validation using the new indices and measures 

* Other additions and modifications
  * Added new function for computing threshold-based joint probability matrices
  * Introduced the use of ff for optimized memory usage in some routines (still under testing)
  * Added new routine for seasonal cycle removal
  * corrMat.VALUE accepting several seasons in the same call
  * Other minor bug fixes and enhancements

